   The Pakistani official also said that on Monday and Tuesday, Indian soldiers fired on Pakistani civilians traveling on a mountain road, injuring four people.
  </a>
  <a href="#5" id="5">
   He also said Indian soldiers fired on an ambulance and a bus.
  </a>
